{"tid":2491944,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"還押與定罪大不同 他們由每日被探訪一次 變每月只得兩次 差無法食射家飯","createTime":"2021-04-16T16:28:20.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-16T16:28:20.000Z","uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"765570a13dc78a2d4e61e3e79dc363a653b8785d","tid":2491944,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T16:28:20.000Z","msg":"壹傳媒創辦人黎智英去年12月被控勾結外國勢力，一度獲准以嚴苛條件短暫保釋，未幾在12月31日除夕夜遭撤回保釋，長期被還押在高度設防的赤柱監獄。隨着法院就8.18和8.31案，宣判黎智英共囚14個月，黎智英在獄中身份亦由「還押人士」變成「定罪在囚人士」，黎的親友每日探訪的場面或不復再。<br />\n<br />\n還押人士可獲親友每天探訪1次，限時15分鐘，每次不得超過2名探訪者；已定罪在囚人士的親友探訪次數則大幅縮減至每月2次，每次限時30分鐘，每次不得超過3名探訪者；但家人可向懲教署申請額外每月2次探訪。<br />\n<br />\n此外，還押人士尚有權向懲教署提出由外界食物供應商提供私人膳食，即俗稱「私家飯」，但若被定罪判刑，此權利便即失去。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210416/2Y2SERNK65HKHIEVKFBGWOCIVM/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR387gzHbfQcz870F0jMWXQ9KBkJsd2tr8R7QC-8R_TL5UAPRoPHEXjWkt8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210416%2F2Y2SERNK65HKHIEVKFBGWOCIVM%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR387gzHbfQcz870F0jMWXQ9KBkJsd2tr8R7QC-8R_TL5UAPRoPHEXjWkt8&d=oTLiiFgDV%2FfsDwDkP3XzLSHfnck7qU2fF1mVfqY7ZMk%3D&h=0dc00288\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210416%2F2Y2SERNK65HKHIEVKFBGWOCIVM%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR387gzHbfQcz870F0jMWXQ9KBkJsd2tr8R7QC-8R_TL5UAPRoPHEXjWkt8&h=833757d8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210416/2Y2SERNK65HKHIEVKFBGWOCIVM/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR387gzHbfQcz870F0jMWXQ9KBkJsd2tr8R7QC-8R_TL5UAPRoPHEXjWkt8</a>"}]}